    </h1>
    <span
      className="Typography__Span-sc-10mju41-0 c2"
    >
      Do not use this unless you have very specific needs for this. For example when you do not want the color to change on light mode. For instance text on background image. 
      <br />
      Use like 
      <pre>
        theme.darkColor.text
      </pre>
    </span>
